{"word":"G2980 - λαλέω - laléō - lal-eh'-o - Preach","slug":"G2980","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">λαλέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>laléō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>lal-eh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Preach"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03BB;&#x03B1;&#x03BB;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - laleo&#x0304;</b> - <i>lal-eh'-o</i><p/>A prolonged form of an otherwise obsolete verb; to <i>talk</i>, that is, <i>utter</i> words: - preach, say, speak (after), talk, tell, utter. Compare <a href=\"#/G3004\">G3004</a>."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1586\">G1586</a>, <a href=\"#/G1588\">G1588</a>, <a href=\"#/G1589\">G1589</a>, <a href=\"#/G249\">G249</a>, <a href=\"#/G3004\">G3004</a>, <a href=\"#/G3050\">G3050</a>, <a href=\"#/G3051\">G3051</a>, <a href=\"#/G3052\">G3052</a>, <a href=\"#/G3054\">G3054</a>, <a href=\"#/G3055\">G3055</a>, <a href=\"#/G3056\">G3056</a>"}]}